Description:
    A planar solid/matrix/solid geometry (SMS), with the SL-SGT EoS that reproduces the adsorbed chain states in Figure 10 in the main document.
Parameters:
    Folder name:                  planar_SMS_SLSGT_Nm100_ra60
    Geometry:                     Planar, SMS
    EoS:                          SL-SGT
    Chain length of m chains:     100
    Polymer-solid potential:      hybrid: Hamaker + ramp
    Critical adsorption distance: 60 Angstrom

